sini/" rel="tag">Gioachino Rossini</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/giorgio-misseri/" rel="tag">Giorgio Misseri</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/jean-pierre-ponnelle/" rel="tag">Jean-Pierre Ponnelle</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/loccasione-fa-il-ladro/" rel="tag">L\'occasione fa il ladro</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/paolo-bordogna/" rel="tag">Paolo Bordogna</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/roberto-de-candia/" rel="tag">Roberto De Candia</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/rossini-opera-festival-2013/" rel="tag">Rossini Opera Festival 2013</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/sonja-frisell/" rel="tag">Sonja Frisell</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/viktoria-yarovaya/" rel="tag">Viktoria Yarovaya</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/yi-chen-lin/" rel="tag">Yi-Chen Lin</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Elena Tsallagova, enea scala, Gioachino Rossini, Giorgio Misseri, Jean-Pierre Ponnelle, L\'occasione fa il ladro, Opera lirica, Paolo Bordogna, Roberto De Candia, Rossini Opera Festival 2013, Sonja Frisell, Viktoria Yarovaya, Yi-Chen Lin"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/b41b40d04cc32e3e4f904f051c19deec" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Michele-Curnis-120x150.jpg" width="80" height="100" alt="Michele Curnis" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Michele Curnis"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/michele-curnis/">View all articles by Michele Curnis</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/08/the-domingo-festival-2/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> The Domingo Festival</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/08/seattle-un-ring-che-avrebbe-reso-wagner-orgoglioso/" rel="next">Seattle: un &#8220;Ring&#8221; che avrebbe reso Wagner orgoglioso <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><h2 class="comments-title"> 1 comment</h2><ol class="commentlist"><li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="li-comment-18349"> <article id="comment-18349" class="comment clearfix"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"><div class="comment-avatar"><img src="http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/d76f38aface0f75d51c8fa91412fa248?s=75&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="75" height="75" alt="" class="avatar avatar-75wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-75 alignnone photo avatar-default" /></div><cite class="fn">tito</cite><a class="comment-meta-time muted-small" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/08/veramente-il-passo-e-ardito-ma-loccasione-fa-il-ladro/#comment-18349"><time datetime="2013-08-25T12:58:52+00:00">25 agosto 2013 at 12:58</time></a> </header> <section class="comment-content comment"><p>Spettacolo godibilissimo, bello l&#8217;allestimento, la musica e bravi i cantanti ed il giovane direttore.<br /> Mi sono piacuti specialmente Enea Scala ed Elena Tsallagova, belle voci pulite e sicure, ma bravi tutti quanti!</p> </section><d